  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2026-02-13",
    "date": "2026-03-03T15:47:49Z",
    "text": "Farm, Food, and National Security Act of 2026\n\nThis bill (commonly known as the farm bill) reauthorizes through FY2031 and modifies Department of Agriculture programs that address\n\ncommodity support,conservation,trade and international food aid,nutrition assistance,farm credit,rural development,research and extension activities,forestry,energy,horticulture,crop insurance,livestock and other animals, andforeign investments in U.S. agricultural land."
  },
